ul.li:
three natural isomorphisms:
\alpha _{x,y,z}: (x \otimes y) \otimes z \simeq x \otimes (y \otimes z), the associator;
\lambda _x: 1_ \otimes \otimes x \simeq x, the left unitor;
\rho _x: x \otimes 1_ \otimes \simeq x, the right unitor.

